Depression isn't "just" sadness. If only.

For a lot of people, it's somehow a combination of sadness, & boredom, & self-blame, & hopelessness, & self-doubt, & did I mention endless, pointless boredom?

Your mileage may vary. But it's almost never just "I'm sad."
#depression

rawContent:
I don’t feel that I can write,
can’t free my soul, depression’s 
grip is too tight.
I’m tied up, help down, up and back.
Stalled in my mind, motivation I lack.
I don’t feel that I can write,
but I do feel. With that I know, 
hope has not left my sight.
#poetry #depression #write
